'''門脈高壓'''（{{lang-en|Portal hypertension}}）為描述{{tsl|en|hepatic portal system|肝門靜脈系統}}高壓的狀態。目前的定義為{{tsl|en|hepatic venous pressure gradient|肝門靜脈梯度}}高於或等於6[[毫米汞柱|mmHg]]<ref>{{Cite web|title = Portal hypertension {{!}} Disease {{!}} Overview {{!}} Genetic and Rare Diseases Information Center (GARD) – an NCATS Program|url = https://rarediseases.info.nih.gov/gard/8229/portal-hypertension/resources/1|website = rarediseases.info.nih.gov|accessdate = 2016-01-08}}</ref>。門脈高壓最常見的原因就是[[肝硬化|肝硬化]]，其他較罕見的原因則稱為'''非肝硬化性門脈高壓'''（{{lang|en|non-cirrhotic portal hypertension}}）。當門脈高壓已造成問題，則必須適當紓解門脈壓力{{citation needed|date=November 2016}}。

==症狀和徵象==
門脈高壓的症狀和徵象包含：
{{columns-list|2|
* [[腹水|腹水]]<ref name=patient/>
** 腹痛或腹脹<ref>{{Cite web|title = Spontaneous Bacterial Peritonitis|url = http://www.karger.com/Article/FullText/84724|website = www.karger.com|accessdate = 2016-01-08}}</ref>，如果合併細菌感染則稱為{{tsl|en|Spontaneous bacterial peritonitis|自發性細菌性腹膜炎}}
* {{tsl|en|Splenomegaly|脾腫大}}<ref name=patient/>，可能導致血小板數量降低
* {{tsl|en|Oesophageal varices|食道靜脈曲張}}，可能破裂導致[[呕血|呕血]]{{citation needed|date=November 2016}}。
* 前腹壁靜脈曲张（有時又稱{{tsl|en|Caput medusae|Caput medusae}}）<ref name=patient/>
* [[痔疮|痔疮]]<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Sun|first1=Z|last2=Migaly|first2=J|title=Review of Hemorrhoid Disease: Presentation and Management.|journal=Clinics in colon and rectal surgery|date=March 2016|volume=29|issue=1|pages=22–9|pmid=26929748|doi=10.1055/s-0035-1568144}}</ref>
}}

